              <path d="m23.93 16.21h-1.8v7.19l6.29 3.77.9-1.47-5.39-3.2z"></path>
             </g> 
            </svg> 
           </picture> <h4 class="h-c-headline h-c-headline--four h-has-bottom-margin"> Deliver faster, smarter marketing. </h4> <p>Built-in intelligence automatically surfaces your most valuable marketing insights so you can act quickly to achieve your goals.</p> </li> 
          <li class="highlights-module__highlight"> <picture> 
