         <p class="h-c-headline h-c-headline--four"> With plenty of free solutions, Google Marketing Platform can help grow businesses of any size. </p> <a data-g-event="for enterprises" data-g-action="see solutions" data-g-label="looking for small business solutions" href="/about/small-business/" class="h-c-button h-c-button--primary" title="See solutions">See solutions</a> 
